comments: Bjelica (SAC) makes incidental contact with DeRozan (SAS) as he legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in Walker IV's (SAS) path during the off-ball screen and makes marginal contact.
Gay (SAS) establishes legal position in Barnes' (SAC) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
Bjelica (SAC) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) on the perimeter and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Holmes (SAC) is firming up in Walker IV's (SAS) path and makes marginal contact during the off-ball screen.
Holmes (SAC) makes marginal contact with White (SAS) during the shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) briefly places a hand to DeRozan's (SAS) front without affecting his SQBR during his drive.
Holmes (SAC) makes contact to DeRozan's (SAS) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Gay (SAS) makes marginal contact with a resting hand to Fox's (SAC) side without extending it or affecting his driving shot attempt.
Bazemore (SAC) makes contact with the ball and cleanly dislodges it from DeRozan (SAS) on the perimeter.
Bazemore (SAC) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) that doesn't affect his SQBR or ability to pass at the end of his drive.
Johnson (SAS) briefly engages and disengages with Bogdanovic (SAC) during the screen.
Hield (SAC) makes marginal contact with Gay (SAS) and doesn't extend or deliver contact that affects his ability to defend the jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
Walker IV (SAS) has a marginal resting hand to Fox's (SAC) body that doesn't affect his shot attempt near the basket.
Bjelica (SAC) commits a take foul on Johnson (SAS).
White (SAS) makes contact with Hield's (SAC) body during his upward shooting motion and affects his jump shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) commits a take foul on White (SAS).
